{"tid":580524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 笑 囡 囡 冇 膽 唱 歌","createTime":"2018-03-04T14:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:46:27.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84630fefc711b2bda7f473c93da6cfb7f687b41c","tid":580524,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）昨日在尖沙嘴為「好時辰世界巡迴演唱會&mdash;香港站」舉行記者會，演唱會將於5月4至5日於香港紅磡體育館舉行。GiGi表示今次以廣東歌為主，香港站只能演出兩天，未能加場。<br />\n<br />\nGiGi指今次沒打算請嘉賓，是一個屬於自己入行二十年回顧的騷，她說：「囡囡冇咁大膽唱到歌，上次拖住佢上台，雙腳已經好似釘住咗喺台度咁。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180303/large/03ec2p20e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180303%2Flarge%2F03ec2p20e.jpg&h=3b736d1c&s={SIZE}\" />b"}]}